### Health API
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### About API
GET http://localhost:8080/api/about
Accept: application/json

###

### Doctors API - list all
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctors
Accept: application/json

###

### Doctors API - filter by department
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctors?department=Internal%20Medicine
Accept: application/json

###

### Doctors API - get one
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D001
Accept: application/json

###

### Doctors API - not found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D999
Accept: application/json

###

### Departments API
GET http://localhost:8080/api/departments
Accept: application/json

###

### Doctors API - create
POST http://localhost:8080/api/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctorId": "D006",
  "name": "Test Doctor",
  "department": "Internal Medicine",
  "specialty": "General Medicine"
}

###

### Doctors API - update
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D006
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Doctor",
  "department": "Internal Medicine",
  "specialty": "General Medicine and Health Check"
}

###

### Doctors API - delete
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D006

###

### Stats page
GET http://localhost:8080/stats
Accept: text/html

###

### Appointments API - count
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/count
Accept: application/json

###

### Appointments API - no query params
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments
Accept: application/json

###

### Appointments API - filter by date
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments?date=2026-05-01
Accept: application/json

###

### Appointments API - filter by doctor id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments?doctorId=D001
Accept: application/json
